Available agreements

  • You can select a maximum of 3 agreements in one recruitment.
  • Ultimately, you may only be qualified for one of the selected trips.
Important

You can only choose agreements for which the deadline for nominations and applications is later than the results of the 4th recruitment (after 20 October this year).
